# Copy to .env and adjust. See comments in the app's api.ts.
#
# Origin of the TechStock backend API.
# Empty  -> same-origin deploy; the app uses relative /api/v1 and /uploads.
# Set    -> cross-origin deploy, e.g. https://api.example.com
#
# Vite inlines this at BUILD time: changing it requires a rebuild/redeploy.
# The backend must list the frontend's origin in CORS_ORIGINS.
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
